OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGenerally cloudy, with perhaps
OL,6,Fsome patchy light rain or drizzle,
OL,7,Fmost likely for western areas.
OL,8,FBrightest in the east, with the best
OL,9,Fchance of some limited bright or sunny
OL,10,Fintervals. Light winds. Slight milder
OL,11,Ffor most places compared to Friday.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry and cloudy start, except
OL,14,Fperhaps some early clear spells across
OL,15,Feastern areas. This evening patchy
OL,16,Flight rain arrives, and persists
OL,17,Fovernight as hill fog develops.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
