OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FOutbreaks of rain initially,
OL,6,Fmainly across northern areas. These
OL,7,Fgradually die away, although taking
OL,8,Fmuch of the day across Derbyshire.
OL,9,FLater bright or sunny spells could
OL,10,Fdevelop across southern areas.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,13,Fovercast with patchy drizzle and early
OL,14,Fhill fog. Tuesday becoming brighter
OL,15,Fwith perhaps showers arriving.
OL,16,FWednesday breezy with sunshine and
OL,17,Fscattered showers. Temperatures close
OL,18,Fto or slightly above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
